  "id": "RAW_8d507c79",
  "title": "AI 被严重低估！AlphaGo 缔造者罕见发声：2026 年 AI 自主上岗 8 小时",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652641723&idx=3&sn=d1a96aa26cb9006fdcdabeaa070725ce",
  "date": "2025-11-04 05:11:00",
